ZH: 我在银行窗口取钱。
EN: I withdraw money at the bank window.

ZH: 请在售票窗口购买车票。
EN: Please buy your train ticket at the ticket window.

ZH: 他透过窗口看着外面的风景。
EN: He looks at the view outside through the window.

ZH: 这个窗口需要修理，因为关不上。
EN: This window needs to be fixed because it won't close.

ZH: 在这个办公室窗口可以缴费。
EN: Payments can be made at the office window.

ZH: 窗口打开时会让阳光照射进来。
EN: Sunlight comes in when the window is open.

ZH: 请到手续办理窗口办理你的签证。
EN: Please go to the visa processing window to apply for your visa.

ZH: 我在窗口前排了很长时间才交上材料。
EN: I waited in line in front of the window for a long time before submitting the documents.

ZH: 他站在窗口边凝视着远方。
EN: He stood by the window gazing into the distance.

ZH: 窗口上贴着通知，告诉大家办公时间。
EN: There is a notice on the window informing everyone of the office hours.

ZH: 售货窗口上有各种美味食物。
EN: The food display window showcases a variety of delicious dishes.

ZH: 这扇窗口装有防盗铁栅。
EN: This window is equipped with anti-theft iron bars.

